41 class RocketLeagueInterface(ROSInterface):
42  """ROS interface for the Rocket League."""
43  def __init__(self, eval=False, launch_file=('rktl_autonomy', 'rocket_league_train.launch'), launch_args=[],
44  run_id=None, env_number=0):
45  super().__init__(node_name='rocket_league_agent', eval=eval, launch_file=launch_file, launch_args=launch_args,
46  run_id=run_id)
47  # Constants
48  self.env_number = env_number
49  # Actions
50  self._MIN_VELOCITY = -rospy.get_param('/cars/throttle/max_speed')
51  self._MAX_VELOCITY = rospy.get_param('/cars/throttle/max_speed')
52  self._MIN_CURVATURE = -tan(rospy.get_param('/cars/steering/max_throw')) / rospy.get_param('cars/length')
53  self._MAX_CURVATURE = tan(rospy.get_param('/cars/steering/max_throw')) / rospy.get_param('cars/length')
54 
55  # Action space overrides
56  if rospy.has_param('~action_space/velocity/min'):
57  min_velocity = rospy.get_param('~action_space/velocity/min')
58  assert min_velocity > self._MIN_VELOCITY
59  self._MIN_VELOCITY = min_velocity
60  if rospy.has_param('~action_space/velocity/max'):
61  max_velocity = rospy.get_param('~action_space/velocity/max')
62  assert max_velocity < self._MAX_VELOCITY
63  self._MAX_VELOCITY = max_velocity
64  if rospy.has_param('~action_space/curvature/min'):
65  min_curvature = rospy.get_param('~action_space/curvature/min')
66  assert min_curvature > self._MIN_CURVATURE
67  self._MIN_CURVATURE = min_curvature
68  if rospy.has_param('~action_space/curvature/max'):
69  max_curvature = rospy.get_param('~action_space/curvature/max')
70  assert max_curvature < self._MAX_CURVATURE
71  self._MAX_CURVATURE = max_curvature
72 
73  # Observations
74  self._FIELD_WIDTH = rospy.get_param('/field/width')
75  self._FIELD_LENGTH = rospy.get_param('/field/length')
76  self._GOAL_DEPTH = rospy.get_param('~observation/goal_depth', 0.075)
77  self._MAX_OBS_VEL = rospy.get_param('~observation/velocity/max_abs', 3.0)
78  self._MAX_OBS_ANG_VEL = rospy.get_param('~observation/angular_velocity/max_abs', 2*pi)
79 
80  # Learning
81  self._MAX_TIME = rospy.get_param('~max_episode_time', 30.0)
82  self._CONSTANT_REWARD = rospy.get_param('~reward/constant', 0.0)
83  self._BALL_DISTANCE_REWARD = rospy.get_param('~reward/ball_dist_sq', 0.0)
84  self._GOAL_DISTANCE_REWARD = rospy.get_param('~reward/goal_dist_sq', 0.0)
85  self._DIRECTION_CHANGE_REWARD = rospy.get_param('~reward/direction_change', 0.0)
86  if isinstance(rospy.get_param('~reward/win', [100.0]), int):
87  self._WIN_REWARD = rospy.get_param('~reward/win', [100.0])
88  else:
89  if len(rospy.get_param('~reward/win', [100.0])) >= self.env_number:
90  self._WIN_REWARD = rospy.get_param('~reward/win', [100.0])[0]
91  else:
92  self._WIN_REWARD = rospy.get_param('~reward/win', [100.0])[self.env_number]
93  if isinstance(rospy.get_param('~reward/loss', [100.0]), int):
94  self._LOSS_REWARD = rospy.get_param('~reward/loss', [100.0])
95  else:
96  if len(rospy.get_param('~reward/loss', [100.0])) >= self.env_number:
97  self._LOSS_REWARD = rospy.get_param('~reward/loss', [100.0])[0]
98  else:
99  self._LOSS_REWARD = rospy.get_param('~reward/loss', [100.0])[self.env_number]
100  self._REVERSE_REWARD = rospy.get_param('~reward/reverse', 0.0)
101  self._WALL_REWARD = rospy.get_param('~reward/walls/value', 0.0)
102  self._WALL_THRESHOLD = rospy.get_param('~reward/walls/threshold', 0.0)
103 
104  # Publishers
105  self._command_pub = rospy.Publisher('cars/car0/command', ControlCommand, queue_size=1)
106  self._reset_srv = rospy.ServiceProxy('sim_reset', Empty)
107 
108  # State variables
109  self._car_odom = None
110  self._ball_odom = None
111  self._score = None
112  self._start_time = None
113  self._prev_vel = None
114 
115  # Subscribers
116  rospy.Subscriber('cars/car0/odom', Odometry, self._car_odom_cb)
117  rospy.Subscriber('ball/odom', Odometry, self._ball_odom_cb)
118  rospy.Subscriber('match_status', MatchStatus, self._score_cb)
119 
120  # block until environment is ready
121  if not eval:
122  rospy.wait_for_service('sim_reset')

124  @property
125  def action_space(self):
126  """The Space object corresponding to valid actions."""
127  return Discrete(CarActions.SIZE)
128 
129  @property
130  def observation_space(self):
131  """The Space object corresponding to valid observations."""
132  return Box(
133  # x, y, theta, v, omega (car)
134  # x, y, vx, vy (ball)
135  low=np.array([
136  -(self._FIELD_LENGTH/2) - self._GOAL_DEPTH,
137  -self._FIELD_WIDTH/2, -pi,
138  -self._MAX_OBS_VEL, -self._MAX_OBS_ANG_VEL,
139  -(self._FIELD_LENGTH/2) - self._GOAL_DEPTH,
140  -self._FIELD_WIDTH/2,
141  -self._MAX_OBS_VEL, -self._MAX_OBS_VEL],
142  dtype=np.float32),
143  high=np.array([
144  (self._FIELD_LENGTH/2) + self._GOAL_DEPTH,
145  self._FIELD_WIDTH/2, pi,
146  self._MAX_OBS_VEL, self._MAX_OBS_ANG_VEL,
147  (self._FIELD_LENGTH/2) + self._GOAL_DEPTH,
148  self._FIELD_WIDTH/2,
149  self._MAX_OBS_VEL, self._MAX_OBS_VEL],
150  dtype=np.float32))
151 
152  def _reset_env(self):
153  """Reset environment for a new training episode."""
154  self._reset_srv.call()
155 
156  def _reset_self(self):
157  """Reset internally for a new episode."""
158  self._clear_state()
159  self._start_time = None
160 
161  def _has_state(self):
162  """Determine if the new state is ready."""
163  return (
164  self._car_odom is not None and
165  self._ball_odom is not None and
166  self._score is not None)
167 
168  def _clear_state(self):
169  """Clear state variables / flags in preparation for new ones."""
170  self._car_odom = None
171  self._ball_odom = None
172  self._score = None
173 
174  def _get_state(self):
175  """Get state tuple (observation, reward, done, info)."""
176  assert self._has_state()
177 
178  # combine car / ball odoms for observation
179  car = np.asarray(self._car_odom, dtype=np.float32)
180  ball = np.asarray(self._ball_odom, dtype=np.float32)
181  observation = np.concatenate((car, ball))
182 
183  # ensure it fits within the observation limits
184  if not self.observation_space.contains(observation):
185  rospy.logwarn_throttle(5, "Coercing observation into valid bounds")
186  np.clip(
187  observation,
188  self.observation_space.low,
189  self.observation_space.high,
190  out=observation)
191 
192  # check if time exceeded
193  if self._start_time is None:
194  self._start_time = rospy.Time.now()
195  done = (rospy.Time.now() - self._start_time).to_sec() >= self._MAX_TIME
196 
197  # Determine reward
198  reward = self._CONSTANT_REWARD
199 
200  ball_dist_sq = np.sum(np.square(ball[0:2] - car[0:2]))
201  reward += self._BALL_DISTANCE_REWARD * ball_dist_sq
202 
203  goal_dist_sq = np.sum(np.square(ball[0:2] - np.array([self._FIELD_LENGTH/2, 0])))
204  reward += self._GOAL_DISTANCE_REWARD * goal_dist_sq
205 
206  if self._score != 0:
207  done = True
208  if self._score > 0:
209  reward += self._WIN_REWARD
210  else:
211  reward += self._LOSS_REWARD
212 
213  x, y, __, v, __ = self._car_odom
214 
215  if self._prev_vel is None:
216  self._prev_vel = v
217  if self._prev_vel * v < 0:
218  reward += self._DIRECTION_CHANGE_REWARD
219  self._prev_vel = v
220 
221  if v < 0:
222  reward += self._REVERSE_REWARD
223  if (abs(x) > self._FIELD_LENGTH/2 - self._WALL_THRESHOLD or
224  abs(y) > self._FIELD_WIDTH/2 - self._WALL_THRESHOLD):
225  reward += self._WALL_REWARD
226 
227  # info dict
228  info = {'goals' : self._score}
229 
230  return (observation, reward, done, info)
231 
232  def _publish_action(self, action):
233  """Publish an action to the ROS network."""
234  assert self.action_space.contains(action)
235 
236  msg = ControlCommand()
237  msg.header.stamp = rospy.Time.now()
238 
239  if ( action == CarActions.FWD or
240  action == CarActions.FWD_RIGHT or
241  action == CarActions.FWD_LEFT):
242  msg.velocity = self._MAX_VELOCITY
243  elif ( action == CarActions.REV or
244  action == CarActions.REV_RIGHT or
245  action == CarActions.REV_LEFT):
246  msg.velocity = self._MIN_VELOCITY
247  else:
248  msg.velocity = 0.0
249 
250  if ( action == CarActions.FWD_LEFT or
251  action == CarActions.REV_LEFT):
252  msg.curvature = self._MAX_CURVATURE
253  elif ( action == CarActions.FWD_RIGHT or
254  action == CarActions.REV_RIGHT):
255  msg.curvature = self._MIN_CURVATURE
256  else:
257  msg.curvature = 0.0
258 
259  self._command_pub.publish(msg)

261  def _car_odom_cb(self, odom_msg):
262  """Callback for odometry of car."""
263  x = odom_msg.pose.pose.position.x
264  y = odom_msg.pose.pose.position.y
265  yaw, __, __ = euler_from_quaternion((
266  odom_msg.pose.pose.orientation.x,
267  odom_msg.pose.pose.orientation.y,
268  odom_msg.pose.pose.orientation.z,
269  odom_msg.pose.pose.orientation.w))
270  v = odom_msg.twist.twist.linear.x
271  omega = odom_msg.twist.twist.angular.z
272 
273  self._car_odom = (x, y, yaw, v, omega)
274 
275  with self._cond:
276  self._cond.notify_all()
277 
278  def _ball_odom_cb(self, odom_msg):
279  """Callback for odometry of ball."""
280  x = odom_msg.pose.pose.position.x
281  y = odom_msg.pose.pose.position.y
282  vx = odom_msg.twist.twist.linear.x
283  vy = odom_msg.twist.twist.linear.y
284 
285  self._ball_odom = (x, y, vx, vy)
286 
287  with self._cond:
288  self._cond.notify_all()
289 
290  def _score_cb(self, score_msg):
291  """Callback for score of game."""
292  if score_msg.status == MatchStatus.VICTORY_TEAM_A:
293  self._score = 1
294  elif score_msg.status == MatchStatus.VICTORY_TEAM_B:
295  self._score = -1
296  else:
297  self._score = 0
298  with self._cond:
299  self._cond.notify_all()
